"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AXvjT","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/6941206439624966152#heading-43\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://juejin.cn/post/6941206439624966152#heading-43</a></p>","author":{"login":"Yill625","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25902472?u=6c538ae2e329c3d72cc724efb03c765ac2d156e5&v=4","url":"https://github.com/Yill625"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYPRi","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">flex一把梭哈</p>","author":{"login":"shabbyaaa","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/48679300?u=ce60faaf13476ef3b0ad1cbac791423ff56bd54d&v=4","url":"https://github.com/shabbyaaa"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYPSg","bodyHTML":"<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">flex布局，无需考虑父子宽高</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"/* 父元素设置 */\ndisplay: flex;\njustify-content: center;\nalign-items: center;\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-c\">/* 父元素设置 */</span>\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> flex;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">justify-content</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">align-items</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">相对定位+transform，无需考虑父子宽高</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"/* 子元素设置 */\nposition: absolute;\ntop: 50%;\nleft: 50%;\ntransform: translate(-50%, -50%);\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-c\">/* 子元素设置 */</span>\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> absolute;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">transform</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">translate</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span><span class=\"pl-kos\">,</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>);</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">display：table-cell</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  width: 500px;\n  height: 500px;\n  background-color: pink;\n  display: table-cell;\n  vertical-align: middle;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.child {\n  width: 200px;\n  height: 200px;\n  background-color: skyblue;\n  display: inline-block;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">width</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">500<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">500<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">background-color</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> pink;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> table-cell;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">vertical-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> middle;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">text-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">child</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">width</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">200<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">200<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">background-color</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> skyblue;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> inline-block;\n}</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">相对定位 + 具体magin</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"position: absolute;\ntop: 50%;\nleft: 50%;\nmargin-top: 手动计算;\nmargin-left: 手动计算;\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> absolute;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n<span class=\"pl-ent\">margin-top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 手动计算;\n<span class=\"pl-ent\">margin-left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 手动计算;</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">magin auto，父元素宽高可以不确定，子元素没有具体宽高会铺满父元素</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"position: absolute;\nmargin: auto;\ntop: 0;\nleft: 0;\nright: 0;\nbottom: 0;\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> absolute;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">margin</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> auto;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">right</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">bottom</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>;</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">手动计算具体magin，父子元素宽高需要确定</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"margin-top: 手动计算;\nmargin-left: 手动计算;\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">margin-top: 手动计算;\nmargin-left: 手动计算;\n</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","author":{"login":"c0dedance","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38075730?v=4","url":"https://github.com/c0dedance"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYQnH","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">方法1：绝对定位+margin:auto<br>\ndiv{<br>\nwidth: 200px;<br>\nheight: 200px;<br>\nbackground: green;</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"    position:absolute;\n    left:0;\n    top: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    margin: auto;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">    position:absolute;\n    left:0;\n    top: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    margin: auto;\n}\n</code></pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法2：绝对定位+负margin<br>\ndiv{<br>\nwidth:200px;<br>\nheight: 200px;<br>\nbackground:green;</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"    position: absolute;\n    left:50%;\n    top:50%;\n    margin-left:-100px;\n    margin-top:-100px;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">    position: absolute;\n    left:50%;\n    top:50%;\n    margin-left:-100px;\n    margin-top:-100px;\n}\n</code></pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法3：绝对定位+transform<br>\ndiv{<br>\nwidth: 200px;<br>\nheight: 200px;<br>\nbackground: green;</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"    position:absolute;\n    left:50%;    /* 定位父级的50% */\n    top:50%;\n    transform: translate(-50%,-50%); /*自己的50% */\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">    position:absolute;\n    left:50%;    /* 定位父级的50% */\n    top:50%;\n    transform: translate(-50%,-50%); /*自己的50% */\n}\n</code></pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法4：flex布局<br>\n.box{<br>\nheight:600px;</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"     display:flex;\n     justify-content:center;  //子元素水平居中\n     align-items:center;      //子元素垂直居中\n       /* aa只要三句话就可以实现不定宽高水平垂直居中。 */\n}\n.box&gt;div{\n    background: green;\n    width: 200px;\n    height: 200px;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">     display:flex;\n     justify-content:center;  //子元素水平居中\n     align-items:center;      //子元素垂直居中\n       /* aa只要三句话就可以实现不定宽高水平垂直居中。 */\n}\n.box&gt;div{\n    background: green;\n    width: 200px;\n    height: 200px;\n}\n</code></pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法5：table-cell实现居中<br>\ndisplay:table-cell;<br>\ntext-align:center;<br>\nvertical-align: middle;</p>","author":{"login":"HXML","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/42664342?u=fdd3b9131d7180d390d5c4fde26cdc5cda621b93&v=4","url":"https://github.com/HXML"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYQ-8","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">1：元素定宽高<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\">position: absolute top: 50% left: 50% transform: translate(-50%, 50%); </code><br>\n2：元素不定宽高<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\">display: flex justify-content: center align-item: center </code></p>","author":{"login":"muyeyong","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/35398394?u=ffd123a87efd623df856c9325cb1cc0ee89c339f&v=4","url":"https://github.com/muyeyong"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYRbZ","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">方法一：绝对定位与负边距（已知宽高）<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\">#container { position: relative; } #center { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; margin: -50px 0 0 -50px; }</code></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法二：绝对定位margin:auto （已知宽高）<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\"> #container { position: relative; height:100px;//必须有个高度 } #center { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; margin: auto;//注意此处的写法 }</code></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法三：绝对定位+css3（未知元素宽高）<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\">  #container { position: relative; } #center { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }</code></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法四：flex<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\"> #container {//直接在父容器设置即可 height: 100vh;//必须有高度 display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }</code></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">方法五：flex/grid和margin: auto<br>\n<code class=\"notranslate\">#container { height: 100vh;//必须有高度 display: grid; } #center { margin: auto; }</code></p>","author":{"login":"CrisChr","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38416380?u=08af1ff184e1e64d06f3de8825b09d32b2201c38&v=4","url":"https://github.com/CrisChr"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYSPh","bodyHTML":"<h2 dir=\"auto\">元素定宽高</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">父元素的宽高为pw,ph。子元素的宽高为cw,ch。</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">流式布局</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".child {\n  margin: calc((ph - ch) / 2) auto;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">child</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">margin</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">calc</span>((ph <span class=\"pl-c1\">-</span> ch) <span class=\"pl-c1\">/</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">2</span>) auto;\n}</pre></div>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">改变元素盒属性</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  line-height: ph;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.child {\n  display: inline-block;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">line-height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> ph;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">text-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">child</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> inline-block;\n}</pre></div>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">元素不定宽高</h2>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">flex大法好</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> flex;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">align-items</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">justify-content</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n}</pre></div>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">绝对定位</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.child {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 50%;\n  left: 50%;\n  transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> relative;\n}\n\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">child</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> absolute;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">transform</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">translateX</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>) <span class=\"pl-en\">translateY</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>);\n}</pre></div>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">table</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n    display: table-cell;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n.child {\n    display: inline-block;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> table-cell;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">vertical-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> middle;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">text-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">child</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> inline-block;\n}</pre></div>","author":{"login":"tangdingga1","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/37588992?u=d2101c2a97ef7a42be34822f2b2c90bc86c744fe&v=4","url":"https://github.com/tangdingga1"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYXMI","bodyHTML":"<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>水平居中\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>inline元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">text-align:center</code>(不需要知道尺寸)</li>\n<li>block元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">margin:auto</code>(不需要知道尺寸)</li>\n<li>absolute元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">left: 50%</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">margin-left:-${自身宽度}/2</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>垂直居中\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>inline元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">line-height:${容器高度}</code></li>\n<li>absolute元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">top:50%</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">margin-top:-${自身高度}/2</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>水平垂直居中\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>flex布局：<code class=\"notranslate\">flex-direction</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">justify-content:center</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">align-items:center</code>(不需要知道尺寸)</li>\n<li>absolute元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">top:50%</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">left:50%</code>+ <code class=\"notranslate\">transform: translate(-50%,-50%)</code>(不需要知道尺寸)\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>CSS3的特性 ，浏览器的兼容性可能会差一点</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>absolute元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">top:0</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">bottom:0</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">left:0</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">right:0</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">margin:auto</code>(不需要知道尺寸)\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>既要保证兼容性，又要保证子元素是未知的，可以用该方法，margin自动填充</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>absolute元素：<code class=\"notranslate\">top:calc(50% - ${高度}/2)</code>+<code class=\"notranslate\">left:calc(50% - ${宽度}/2)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","author":{"login":"goodmornight","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17687454?u=051ebe194d376b7eec4f657d5ad989491884dba3&v=4","url":"https://github.com/goodmornight"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AYhLs","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">不定宽高的居中方式, 这些居中元素的大小可以被内容撑开，依旧保持居中</p>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>flex布局</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".container {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">container</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> flex;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">align-items</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">justify-content</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n}</pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\" dir=\"auto\">\n<li>inline-block布局</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".container {\n    text-align: center;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n}\n.container::before {\n    content: &quot;&quot;;\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 0;\n    height: 100%;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n}\n.center-box {\n    display: inline-block;\n    line-height: 100%;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n    border: 1px solid red;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">container</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">text-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> center;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">white-space</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> nowrap;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">container</span>::<span class=\"pl-ent\">before</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">content</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\">\"\"</span>;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> inline-block;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">width</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">100<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">vertical-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> middle;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">center-box</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> inline-block;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">line-height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">100<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">vertical-align</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> middle;\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">border</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">1<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span> solid red;\n}</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">需要确定宽高的居中方式：<br>\n3. position + margin</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".container {\n   position: relative;\n}\n.center-box {\n    width: ...;\n    height: ...;\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    margin: auto;\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">container</span> {\n   <span class=\"pl-c1\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> relative;\n}\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">center-box</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">width</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> ...;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> ...;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">position</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">absolute</span>;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 0;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">bottom</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 0;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 0;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">right</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 0;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">margin</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">auto</span>;\n}</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">4.transform</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".center-box {\n    width: ...;\n    height: ...;\n    margin-top: 50%;\n    margin-left: 50%;\n    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">.<span class=\"pl-c1\">center-box</span> {\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">width</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> ...;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> ...;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">margin-top</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 50%;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">margin-left</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> 50%;\n    <span class=\"pl-ent\">transform</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">translate</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span><span class=\"pl-kos\">,</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">-50<span class=\"pl-smi\">%</span></span>)\n}</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">兼容性方面，应该是2和3兼容性最好，但是超出父元素大小的时候会对齐在左上角。<br>\n附上codepen：<a href=\"https://codepen.io/blackcoffeecat/pen/MWrmWmX\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://codepen.io/blackcoffeecat/pen/MWrmWmX</a></p>","author":{"login":"blackcoffeecat","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43604283?v=4","url":"https://github.com/blackcoffeecat"},"replies":null}},{"node":{"id":"IC_kwDOHCfdf85AxM9b","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">grid 最简洁</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><code class=\"notranslate\">.parent{ display:grid; place-items:center; }</code></p>","author":{"login":"iKeepLearn","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38156393?u=d8292c6c5e10957d4f88c4c6f069de2c1580c000&v=4","url":"https://github.com/iKeepLearn"},"replies":null}}]}}},"pageContext":{"number":26,"previous":{"title":"